==English==
===Pronunciation===
/'…Ļ…õd.…õks/

/ňą…Ļiňźd…õks/

===Etymology===
From "[[red]] [[X]]"

From "[[reduce|reducible]] [[expression]]"

===Verb===
'''redex'''

#(''Internet'') of an image, to display a red X rather than the intended image; to fail to load

===Noun===
'''redex''' <!-- Note: Different etym and pron. -->

#(''mathematics'') Something to be [[reduce]]d according to the rules of a formal system.

===Usage notes===
The verb form is from "red X" and is properly pronounced " /r…õd…õks/;
the noun form is from "reducible expression" and is properly pronounced /ňąriňźd…õks/.

